{"tid":1594022,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[長文]喂，老老實實，D放負撚同分化割席有咩分別?","createTime":"2019-09-25T10:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T11:22:54.000Z","uid":4857,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"78c727a9bc005e5c74acda16026ab273ac4205e8","tid":1594022,"uid":4857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:47:09.000Z","msg":"最近見到愈黎愈多人放負，有感而發想講幾句:(TLDR係最底!)<br />\n<br />\n好多人最近開始係度屌其他人無行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 又話咩<span style=\"color: red;\">淨係識係屋企睇新聞好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>, 又話<span style=\"color: green;\">D都勇武唔敢搞POPO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>, 又話<span style=\"color: blue;\">D人好呢樣唔敢果樣唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>...<br />\n<br />\n1. 社運唔係鬥激進,係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">爭取共識</span></span>:<br />\n首先, 我地出黎爭取<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></span>, 要令呢件事得以成功, 係要證明好多人都同意呢五個訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 而要證明好多人都支持, 第一步係真係要有好多人支持, 呢個第一步我地而家係做到, 但係之後點呢? 我認為而家既<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">戰線已經遠超街頭抗爭</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />; 唔係你<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">遊行</span></span>, 甚至<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">衝</span></span>, 甚至放<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">火魔法</span></span>可以打得羸既杖! 但係點解我地繼續做? 係因為我地要強調, <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人心未死</span></span>, 你唔回應五大訴求, 我地就唔會收聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!<br />\n<br />\n2. 你身邊愈多呢D支持你而無乜行動, 或者無你行得咁前既人, 代表D乜:<br />\n跟住好多人就會覺得, 我身邊邊個邊個無行動喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 佢淨係口講支持, 日日有FOLLOW, 但你又唔出黎, 久而久之, 甚至嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />左呢D人, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">覺得佢地虛作無聲</span></span>, 無貢獻等等...612遊行果陣, 我同我朋友(我地都有FOLLOW下政治野) 見到好多<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">奇景</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 例如D人<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對民主黨鼓掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 對住人民力量叫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 叫社民連加油等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>...呢個時候, 我身邊有一個人同佢朋友講, 呢班人真係唔識架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />! <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TFYMMb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTFYMMb6.jpg&h=900cf595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢個朋友話, 其實<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">愈多唔識既人出到黎, 咪即係呢件事係愈多人同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 連呢D平時係港豬既人都出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>, 反而係一個好好既現像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(即係我地之前成日講既<span style=\"color: gold;\">WE CONNECT!</span>)<br />\n<br />\n3. 點解放負等於割席; 或者點解諷刺唔會令人團結:<br />\n咁點解放負撚就等於割席呢? 首先, 你要接受你身邊好多人無你咁關心政治, 咁佢地之前真係港豬黎架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />! 佢地出左黎FOLLOW大家, 大家其實應該<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好好地引導呢班人</span></span>, 而唔係話佢知你做唔到咩咩咩就唔岩, 唔好, 甚至係度泠言泠語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />! 大家要明白, 而家既情況, 就<span style=\"color: green;\">好似你屋企入面既老人家, 岩岩學識用SMARTPHONE, 咩都唔識, 其實佢地好需要你幫手, 佢地有問題, 或者有疑惑, 未必會即時問你, 可能收收埋埋, 就係因為驚比你講句&quot;下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 乜你咁都唔識&quot;! </span>佢地亦都好多野係唔敢做, 唔會做, 叫極都唔做! 點解? 因為呢件事離開左佢地既COMFORT ZONE囉! 佢地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">驚</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呀! 你可能覺得當獨裁成為事實, 革命就是義務! 但係佢地驚架嘛! 3個月之前佢地豬黎架咋! 如果你因為咁樣就PUSH AWAY佢地, 咁係咪割左人地席先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />! 你估真係數碼暴龍, 遇怪魔我<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">即刻</span></span>變大個咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />? 一個人成長係經驗累積, <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要好多時間架!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n4. 咁應該點做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />? 讚佢地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n咁又唔使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 不過要明白一件事, 就係唔係世界圍繞住我地轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 係我地要跟住世界轉! 點解當初勇武可以由後生居多, 變左後來既十八區勇武街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 除左因為勇武本身真係街坊, 亦係因為我地跟住件事轉! 將一件<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">相對難</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />既事(行上示威區勇武), 變成一件<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">入到口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>既事(落樓下屌走POPO)! 我地應該做既, 係為係唔脂階段既人, 製造一D容易比佢地入到口支持既事! <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你完全唔郁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />? 不如睇下TWITTER啦, 哦你有睇開架, 咁你有冇開ACC, LIKE下, 轉推下呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />? 哦你都有架, 咁你有冇出去聲援下D地區活動, 放映會, 參加下大合唱呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哦原來你都有拿, 咁你會唔會貼下文宣, 參加下地區行動架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />? 哦都會拿, 咁平時大大少少遊行有冇出席呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />? 社運係咁樣一步一步行出黎架!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後, 我想同大家講, <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">正面既鼓勵, 係比負面既諷刺更有效</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 最近有好多事, 係呢一代既香港人都未遇過, 包括前無古人既示威活動, 無法無天既黑警濫暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 被捕者不知去向既疑雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 滿天飛不知真假既傳言等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 我認為香港人係呢D時候更要團結, 唔好因為他人做得比你少, 怯於做某D野就屌人, <br />\n要互相扶助, <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不分化, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不割席, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不篤魁</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\nTLDR: 社運係要爭取共識, 你見到好多人做好多低能行為, 或者無行動, 係因為呢班人未必係唔想做, 可能係時辰未到, 但如果你地係度放負, 就一定會打擊佢地向前行一步既信心! 我地一路走來都係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不分化, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不割席, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不篤魁! 六月如是, 今日如是!</span></span>"},{"pid":"5df0fc1e802217fb3ccabd04ce398454bc6d2349","tid":1594022,"uid":4857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:50:00.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"103d980cbf59a344d431057e482ef7e21177313c","tid":1594022,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:51:38.000Z","msg":"日日講推post,真係咁撚有心就落街派傳單啦，上得連登邊有可能冇日程表，除非係本身就點都唔會去嗰班<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n證明有死人你一樣吹佢唔漲，冇死人一樣要追究濫權同雙普選<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1593389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1593389</a>"},{"pid":"5e27e1437e966a8d5386b61dd0e8001f19c5cd64","tid":1594022,"uid":4857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:55:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c50d09c8aa4f7e7d862ed29f2169b50c6e05a6e","tid":1594022,"uid":182185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d32137be1f11d63c696dd34891c8644694720d0","tid":1594022,"uid":4857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T11:00:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62c2cd8048c30de24a15c6fc955552deb546c4ec","tid":1594022,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T11:02:00.000Z","msg":"最精彩放負撚<br />\n<br />\n舉美國旗美國人反感<br />\n<br />\n共產黨反感炸掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e525072e9bb0122accc1d22125580899e22a0a7a","tid":1594022,"uid":4857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62c2cd8048c30de24a15c6fc955552deb546c4ec","tid":1594022,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T11:02:00.000Z","msg":"最精彩放負撚<br />\n<br />\n舉美國旗美國人反感<br />\n<br />\n共產黨反感炸掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T11:02:36.000Z","msg":"果D算係風向撚啦, 分分鐘五毛黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cfefd95bf8894cc275409dee198899c49e95297","tid":1594022,"uid":4857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T11:10:46.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"3b10363d3f775d3050bb4de55d109ebb6afa6533","tid":1594022,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T11:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad71b2648bb9072c0a0002b025339ab8db036f71","tid":1594022,"uid":4857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T11:20:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f05fea5c34b298c59b519579dbffbadd3ac667cb","tid":1594022,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T11:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫推"}]}